common and device-specific sysfs attwibutes fow switches. Because switches awe
integwated into the WapidIO subsystem, it offews a method to cweate
device-specific sysfs attwibutes by specifying a cawwback function that may be
set by the switch initiawization woutine duwing enumewation ow discovewy
pwocess.

